{"tid":688214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件耶撚膠事","createTime":"2018-06-03T04:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T08:00:35.000Z","uid":174946,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"883d6c7870b4b3eb8ea6f934a4c70abdff008c39","tid":688214,"uid":174946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"早排同朋友打牌而其中一個係耶撚嚟<br />\n好似近排日日返教會<br />\n到中途打打吓牌佢就發咗癲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 耶撚<br />\n當佢入章嘅時候<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 正！入章係上帝嘅安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當佢做啱章嘅時候<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：好彩上帝帶領我行條正確嘅道路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當佢成手爛牌嘅時候<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係上帝俾我嘅試練 就好似摩西咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當佢自摸嘅時候<br />\n摸完牌之後無啦啦喺度祈禱 之後先喊自摸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：上帝真係對我不薄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到最後佢真係贏得最多嗰個<br />\n我哋三個望住佢嗰個誠懇嘅耶撚樣<br />\n已經分唔清佢係真膠定假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68260710055ca1b9de028409930d606d0e7fd11e","tid":688214,"uid":174946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:37:15.000Z","msg":"近排刨書研究佛經 下次同佢決一死戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6099cb679ca430a15453ea438e3614ba7c9bb6","tid":688214,"uid":174946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd2092eeafc72c9002e5ee995d42336a74c2354","tid":688214,"uid":174946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cde898706b6890742f22137062a5c15d103f273","tid":688214,"uid":174946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c05b94f5c0e82ce6aea102c7120c82bf6a4291e","tid":688214,"uid":174946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}